{"tid":2303557,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–全球變暖反而使樹葉提前變黃","createTime":"2020-11-28T05:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T15:19:46.000Z","uid":38861,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"92a693cb6e4299ae6e16aababf27f7250a50865e","tid":2303557,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:13:25.000Z","msg":"陽光、二氧化碳及水份充足情況下，光合作用在樹葉裡頭發生，二氧化碳的碳原子將儲存在樹木裡，並釋出氧氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72d62db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72d62db.jpg&h=e84cf18b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n秋天時份，溫度驟降，樹木意識到冬天即將來臨，便啟動落葉機制，以免冬天低溫為樹葉帶來傷害。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）根據這個理念，全球氣侯所導致的溫度提升，將會使綠葉時間延長1-3星期。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UjzxXMF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUjzxXMF.jpg&h=22ca9ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但出乎意外的是，實驗及現實證據指出，綠葉時間反而是平均縮短了3-6日（Ref1)。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）分析由1948-2015年達434,226項的樹木數據再加上各種實驗，科學家得出以下的解釋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qq2cdkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqq2cdkd.jpg&h=26030e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球變暖再加上大氣二氧化碳含量上升，樹木的光合代謝率亦因而有所提升。<br />\n<br />\n光合代謝的過程中，二氧化碳的碳原子會以固體方式儲存在榭木內。<br />\n如果固體碳原子到達一定的程度，就算溫度和暖，亦會觸發樹葉變黃及落葉發生。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）圖中展示出兩種導致落葉情況發生的可能性。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QRnfVyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQRnfVyB.jpg&h=7cdcb975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這表示出每一棵樹木均有其轉化二氧化碳至氧氣的限額，並不能夠無窮無盡地吸收二氧化碳。<br />\n單純依靠種植樹木意圖來改善全球的氣候變化，實際上亦有一定的限制。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CqNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=ab3d85f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/370/6520/1066?intcmp=trendmd-sci\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F370%2F6520%2F1066%3Fintcmp%3Dtrendmd-sci&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CqNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=bc1d593f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/370/6520/1066?intcmp=trendmd-sci</a>"},{"pid":"4b80da604d101d7ca5fb8c959299c1c7db6d8fc1","tid":2303557,"uid":380296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"92a693cb6e4299ae6e16aababf27f7250a50865e","tid":2303557,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:13:25.000Z","msg":"陽光、二氧化碳及水份充足情況下，光合作用在樹葉裡頭發生，二氧化碳的碳原子將儲存在樹木裡，並釋出氧氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72d62db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72d62db.jpg&h=e84cf18b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n秋天時份，溫度驟降，樹木意識到冬天即將來臨，便啟動落葉機制，以免冬天低溫為樹葉帶來傷害。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）根據這個理念，全球氣侯所導致的溫度提升，將會使綠葉時間延長1-3星期。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UjzxXMF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUjzxXMF.jpg&h=22ca9ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但出乎意外的是，實驗及現實證據指出，綠葉時間反而是平均縮短了3-6日（Ref1)。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）分析由1948-2015年達434,226項的樹木數據再加上各種實驗，科學家得出以下的解釋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qq2cdkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqq2cdkd.jpg&h=26030e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球變暖再加上大氣二氧化碳含量上升，樹木的光合代謝率亦因而有所提升。<br />\n<br />\n光合代謝的過程中，二氧化碳的碳原子會以固體方式儲存在榭木內。<br />\n如果固體碳原子到達一定的程度，就算溫度和暖，亦會觸發樹葉變黃及落葉發生。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）圖中展示出兩種導致落葉情況發生的可能性。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QRnfVyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQRnfVyB.jpg&h=7cdcb975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這表示出每一棵樹木均有其轉化二氧化碳至氧氣的限額，並不能夠無窮無盡地吸收二氧化碳。<br />\n單純依靠種植樹木意圖來改善全球的氣候變化，實際上亦有一定的限制。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CqNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=ab3d85f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/370/6520/1066?intcmp=trendmd-sci\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F370%2F6520%2F1066%3Fintcmp%3Dtrendmd-sci&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CqNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=bc1d593f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/370/6520/1066?intcmp=trendmd-sci</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0730602c2b0dada08b6c13ce5380b79975da8c63","tid":2303557,"uid":192776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6c64034c47b269bea2f9e1052f9042339ba738","tid":2303557,"uid":26028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd0e68c1eeeb4f84e4282e2b1d30e6e8c4798b99","tid":2303557,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:22:17.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"fda8e6034cbf4cbf712280655d11773432aace13","tid":2303557,"uid":72730,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403ad2a21ef1c1a16972073e4175a2a71cee8689","tid":2303557,"uid":65031,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:24:19.000Z","msg":"Followed"},{"pid":"cdb4529e8b202270f6de80bf2310ac42d7eb3edb","tid":2303557,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"有冇啲植物全年綠色"},{"pid":"d1661e4671ca638bd420caf75c5af5a21f0e8710","tid":2303557,"uid"